## 💡 Key Concepts Demonstrated

- **Event-driven security automation** — no manual polling, no cron jobs
- **Serverless architecture** — zero infrastructure to manage
- **Least-privilege IAM** — Lambda only has permission to publish to one SNS topic
- **Threat simulation** — using AWS CLI to generate sample findings for safe testing
- **Human-readable alerting** — transforming raw machine output into actionable notifications

